citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:45 pm on
08-Feb-18.
The inspector arrived at the facility at 1:45 pm and knocked on the door to the house, honked the car horn, and
called the facility's phone number and left a message. The inspector waited 30 minutes and then left the facility.
